                        <div class="btn-art-simple-ctr"><a href="<?=  base_url()?>assets/resume-templates">Create My Resume Now</a></div>
                        <p>The <strong>first version</strong> that we have <a href="http://www.businessinsider.com/elons-musk-resume-all-on-one-page-2016-4?r=US&amp;IR=T&amp;IR=T" target="_blank">created in 2016 proving the concept “Less, is More!”</a> which inspired many persons to reduce the length of their resumes and impress recruiters is the following: </p>
